articles.title: Reddit shares surge as it strikes content deal with OpenAI - Financial Times
articles.description: Agreement comes as competition for high-quality data to underpin AI models intensifies
articles.content: OpenAI has struck a deal with Reddit to use content from the social media platform for its artificial intelligence chatbot, sending shares in the company up as much as 15 per cent in after-hours trad… [+3744 chars]
